trans-unit.source: Represents the radii of a rectangle's corners.
trans-unit.target: Representa os raios dos cantos do retângulo.

trans-unit.source: This class has four properties, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A>, corresponding to the individual corners of the rectangle.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe tem quatro propriedades, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A>, e <xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A>, correspondendo ao individuais cantos do retângulo.</xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomRight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.BottomLeft%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopRight%2A> </xref:System.Windows.CornerRadius.TopLeft%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each is a <xref:System.Double> structure that can be set independently of the others.
trans-unit.target: Cada um é um <xref:System.Double>estrutura que pode ser definida independentemente de outras pessoas.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: The radii cannot be negative.
trans-unit.target: Os raios não podem ser negativos.

trans-unit.source: ## XAML Attribute Usage ``` - or - ``` ## XAML Values *TopLeft* value that specifies the radius of the top left corner.
trans-unit.target: # # Uso do atributo XAML ``` - or - ``` # # XAML valores *TopLeft* valor que especifica o raio da parte superior esquerda.

trans-unit.source: *TopRight* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the top right corner.
trans-unit.target: *TopRight* <xref:System.Double> valor que especifica o canto superior direito.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *BottomRight* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the bottom right corner.
trans-unit.target: *BottomRight* <xref:System.Double> valor que especifica o canto inferior direito.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *BottomLeft* <xref:System.Double> value that specifies the bottom left corner.
trans-unit.target: *BottomLeft* <xref:System.Double> valor que especifica o canto inferior esquerdo.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: *AllCorners* If only a single <xref:System.Double> value is specified, that measure is applied to ALL of the *TopLeft*, *TopRight*, *BottomRight*, and *BottomLeft* corners of the CornerRadius.
trans-unit.target: *AllCorners* se um único <xref:System.Double>valor for especificado, o que a medida é aplicada a todos os *TopLeft*, *TopRight*, *BottomRight*, e *BottomLeft* cantos do CornerRadius.</xref:System.Double>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Values need not include the decimal point explicitly when specified as a string.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Valores não precisam incluir o ponto decimal explicitamente quando especificado como uma cadeia de caracteres.

trans-unit.source: The string "1" provided in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] evaluates to a value of 1.0 when referenced in code.
trans-unit.target: A cadeia de caracteres "1" fornecido no [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] é avaliada como um valor de 1,0 quando referenciado no código.
